    {
      "id": "PopularPost184467",
      "post_content": "Are you kids crazy?? If this thing was any cheaper or better it would be brokenly powerful!\n  \n   \nCompare with [Dark Banishing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Banishing). For two more mana (and based on the kind of things you *should* be using this on) you could be getting anywhere from 3-8 life or more. Plus if your opponent knows you have it somewhere in your deck they'll be scared to drop their big beasties until it's taken care of - the kind of beasties they'd be dropping around oh, I don't know, turn 5 maybe? Plus as a sorcery you won't be paranoid about saving enough mana to use it whenever, unlike an instant...\n  \n   \nOverall, a very underrated card.",
      "posted_by": "Villainous1",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost184467\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Are you kids crazy?? If this thing was any cheaper or better it would be brokenly powerful!\r<br/> <br/>Compare with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dark Banishing\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Banishing\">Dark Banishing</a>. For two more mana (and based on the kind of things you <i>should</i> be using this on) you could be getting anywhere from 3-8 life or more. Plus if your opponent knows you have it somewhere in your deck they'll be scared to drop their big beasties until it's taken care of - the kind of beasties they'd be dropping around oh, I don't know, turn 5 maybe? Plus as a sorcery you won't be paranoid about saving enough mana to use it whenever, unlike an instant...\r<br/> <br/>Overall, a very underrated card.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '184467'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy65351\">Villainous1</span>\r\n                                (8/2/2011 6:37:26 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\"