      "id": "PopularPost189845",
      "post_content": "No, this card is just bad, and it wouldn't be broken even if it cost 2B. Why would any competitive player ever use this over, say, Doom Blade? The non-regeneration clause is highly situational, sorcery speed is in fact a disadvantage and not an advantage like you seem to think, and life gain alone is not worth an extra three mana, even if you do gain 6+ life off of it. This card would be a fine casual card at 2BB, instant speed, destroy any creature, but as it is it's not even worth running in casual.",
      "posted_by": "Henrietta",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost189845\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">No, this card is just bad, and it wouldn't be broken even if it cost 2B. Why would any competitive player ever use this over, say, Doom Blade? The non-regeneration clause is highly situational, sorcery speed is in fact a disadvantage and not an advantage like you seem to think, and life gain alone is not worth an extra three mana, even if you do gain 6+ life off of it. This card would be a fine casual card at 2BB, instant speed, destroy any creature, but as it is it's not even worth running in casual.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '189845'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy59501\">Henrietta</span>\r\n                                (8/21/2011 11:13:01 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/S